Using the Ads Preferences Manager, you can edit the list of inferred interest and demographic categories that Google has associated with your cookie or opt-out of the cookie entirely. All information Google gathers is used in accordance with Google's privacy policy and helps Google improve your online experience. It is not used to identify you personally and Google will not show interest-based ads based on personal information without your permission.
